Description: Stormware's Pohoda XML/PHP serialization
 This library provides a PHP-based solution for serializing
 and deserializing XML data for Stormware's Pohoda accounting
 software. It is designed to work with Pohoda's XML schema
 definitions (XSD) and simplifies the process of integrating
 Pohoda's data exchange into your PHP applications.
